[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      354[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      355[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         features = empty map
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         FOR each modality_vol in registered_volumes:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             modality_features = extract radiomic features:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                 first_order   = [mean, std, skewness, kurtosis, entropy]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      359[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                 shape         = [volume, surface_area, sphericity, compactness]
